author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Join me, MauLer, Snarky Jay, Star Wars Theory, Robot Head and Chris Gore as we delve once more into the world of Andor. And cover The Last Of Us' hugely divisive second episode, plus the Predator Badlands trailer.
